'''毛里求斯艷織雀'''（學名：''{{lang|la|Foudia rubra}}''）是[[织布鸟科|织布鸟科]]的一種罕有的[[鳥類|鳥類]]，是[[毛里求斯|毛里求斯]]的[[特有種|特有種]]。[[國際鳥盟|國際鳥盟]]<ref name=birdlife>{{cite web |url=http://www.birdlife.org/datazone/species/index.html?action=SpcHTMDetails.asp&sid=8576&m=0 |title=BirdLife International Species Fact Sheet |accessdate=2010-11-24 |archive-date=2009-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090103085557/http://www.birdlife.org/datazone/species/index.html?action=SpcHTMDetails.asp&sid=8576&m=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[美國魚類及野生動物管理局|美國魚類及野生動物管理局]]<ref name="fws">{{cite web |author=[[美國魚類及野生動物管理局|美國魚類及野生動物管理局]] |url=http://ecos.fws.gov/docs/federal_register/fr2771.pdf |title=Addition of 30 African birds to list of endangered and threatened wildlife |publisher=''Federal Register'' |date=1995-01-12 |accessdate=2019-08-19 |archive-date=2011-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111018030321/http://ecos.fws.gov/docs/federal_register/fr2771.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>均把本物種分類為[[瀕危物種|瀕危物種]]；而[[國際自然保護聯盟|國際自然保護聯盟]]將牠們列為[[瀕危|瀕危]]，估計其數量少於250隻<ref name=iucn/>。牠們主要是受到失去棲息地及[[入侵物種|入侵物種]]的威脅<ref>{{Cite web |title=Mauritits Fody |authors=Durrell Wildlife Conservation Trust |url=http://www.durrell.org/Animals/Birds/Mauritius-fody/ |date=2009-02-11 |access-date=2010-11-24 |archive-date=2011-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111107065345/http://www.durrell.org/Animals/Birds/Mauritius-fody/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

{{tsl|en|Île aux Aigrettes|白鹭岛 (毛里求斯)|白鹭岛}}（{{lang|fr|Île aux Aigrettes}}），毛里求斯主島以外的一個小島，現時是不少毛里求斯艷織雀及其他受威脅物種的重置家園<ref name=garr>Garrett, L. (2009). [http://www.africanbirdclub.org/countries/MauritiusandRodrigues/documents/MauritiusFodyAnnualReport2008-09Sept2009.pdf Mauritian Wildlife Foundation Mauritius Fody Recovery Programme Annual Report 2008-09.] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120527114003/http://www.africanbirdclub.org/countries/MauritiusandRodrigues/documents/MauritiusFodyAnnualReport2008-09Sept2009.pdf |date=2012-05-27 }}</ref>。

